org.goobi.production.flow.statistics.hibernate

Class StatQuestProjectProgressData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.goobi.production.flow.statistics.hibernate.StatQuestProjectProgressData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IStatisticalQuestion, IStatisticalQuestionLimitedTimeframe

    public class StatQuestProjectProgressData
extends Object
implements IStatisticalQuestionLimitedTimeframe, Serializable
    Imlpementation of IStatisticalQuestion. This is used for the generation of a Datatable relfecting the progress of a project, based on it's processes workflow. Only the workflow common to all processes is used. A reference step is taken and it's progress is calculated against the average throughput. The average throughput is based on the duration and volume of a project.
    Author:
    Wulf Riebensahm
